Title: The Giant Spider Invasion
Writer: Richard L. Huff (screenplay), Robert Easton (screenplay), Richard L. Huff (original story)
Actors: Steve Brodie, Barbara Hale, Robert Easton, Leslie Parrish
Plot: A black hole hits North Wisconsin and opens a door to other dimensions. Giant 15 meter spiders emerge from it, who have an appetite for human flesh! Dr. Jenny Langer and Dr. Vance from the NASA try to save the world.
